<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
gimpunit

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
Provides a collection of predefined units and functions for creating
user-defined units.

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
Provides a collection of predefined units and functions for creating
user-defined units.

</para>

